  "title": "Preschool Cleaner (part time)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Part-Time Cleaner</strong></h2>\n<p>Are you a passionate cleaner looking for a rewarding part-time opportunity? A vibrant preschool in Singapore is seeking a dedicated <strong>Part-Time Cleaner</strong> to join our team!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>· General cleaning (sweeping, mopping, vacuuming, etc.)</p>\n<p>· Cleaning of toilets, pantry and common area</p>\n<p>· Disposing of rubbish</p>\n<p>· Replenish toiletries when needed</p>\n<p>· Maintain cleanliness and hygiene standards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Be part of a warm and supportive preschool environment.</li>\n  <li>Flexible part-time hours.</li>\n  <li>Contribute directly to the well-being of young children.</li>\n  <li>Short working hours everyday 9am to 3.30pm (Monday to Friday only), with 30mins lunch break in between. Working hours can be discussed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have a passion for celaning and love working in a child-friendly environment, we'd love to hear from you!</p>\n<p><strong>To Apply:</strong> Please send your resume to [enquiry@noblelandarts-learning.com.sg] or call [63480024] for more information.</p>",
